{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.1","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:1","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.001.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les faux docteurs<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. Ac 20:29, 30. Jud v. 3-7. Ap 2:14, 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Il y a eu parmi le peuple de faux proph\u00e8tes, et il y aura de m\u00eame parmi vous de faux docteurs, qui introduiront des sectes pernicieuses, et qui, reniant le ma\u00eetre qui les a rachet\u00e9s, attireront sur eux une ruine soudaine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.2","name":"2 Pierre 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.1.21","name":"2 Pierre 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.1.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.2","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:2","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Plusieurs les suivront dans leurs dissolutions, et la voie de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 sera calomni\u00e9e \u00e0 cause d\u2019eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.3","name":"2 Pierre 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.1","name":"2 Pierre 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.3","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:3","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Par cupidit\u00e9, ils trafiqueront de vous au moyen de paroles trompeuses, eux que menace depuis longtemps la condamnation, et dont la ruine ne sommeille point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.4","name":"2 Pierre 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.2","name":"2 Pierre 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.4","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:4","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Car, si Dieu n\u2019a pas \u00e9pargn\u00e9 les anges qui ont p\u00e9ch\u00e9, mais s\u2019il les a pr\u00e9cipit\u00e9s dans les ab\u00eemes de t\u00e9n\u00e8bres et les r\u00e9serve pour le jugement;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.5","name":"2 Pierre 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.3","name":"2 Pierre 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.5","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:5","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>s\u2019il n\u2019a pas \u00e9pargn\u00e9 l\u2019ancien monde, mais s\u2019il a sauv\u00e9 No\u00e9, lui huiti\u00e8me, ce pr\u00e9dicateur de la justice, lorsqu\u2019il fit venir le d\u00e9luge sur un monde d\u2019impies;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.6","name":"2 Pierre 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.4","name":"2 Pierre 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.6","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:6","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>s\u2019il a condamn\u00e9 \u00e0 la destruction et r\u00e9duit en cendres les villes de Sodome et de Gomorrhe, les donnant comme exemple aux impies \u00e0 venir,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.7","name":"2 Pierre 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.5","name":"2 Pierre 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.7","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:7","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>et s\u2019il a d\u00e9livr\u00e9 le juste Lot, profond\u00e9ment attrist\u00e9 de la conduite de ces hommes sans frein dans leur dissolution<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.8","name":"2 Pierre 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.6","name":"2 Pierre 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.8","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:8","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>(car ce juste, qui habitait au milieu d\u2019eux, tourmentait journellement son \u00e2me juste \u00e0 cause de ce qu\u2019il voyait et entendait de leurs \u0153uvres criminelles);<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.9","name":"2 Pierre 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.7","name":"2 Pierre 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.9","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:9","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>le Seigneur sait d\u00e9livrer de l\u2019\u00e9preuve les hommes pieux, et r\u00e9server les injustes pour \u00eatre punis au jour du jugement,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.10","name":"2 Pierre 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.8","name":"2 Pierre 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.10","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:10","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>ceux surtout qui vont apr\u00e8s la chair dans un d\u00e9sir d\u2019impuret\u00e9 et qui m\u00e9prisent l\u2019autorit\u00e9. Audacieux et arrogants, ils ne craignent pas d\u2019injurier les gloires,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.11","name":"2 Pierre 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.9","name":"2 Pierre 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.11","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:11","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-22: cf. (Jud v. 8-19. 2 Ti 3:1-9, 13.) Mt 12:43-45.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>tandis que les anges, sup\u00e9rieurs en force et en puissance, ne portent pas contre elles de jugement injurieux devant le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.12","name":"2 Pierre 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.10","name":"2 Pierre 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.12","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:12","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Mais eux, semblables \u00e0 des brutes qui s\u2019abandonnent \u00e0 leurs penchants naturels et qui sont n\u00e9es pour \u00eatre prises et d\u00e9truites, ils parlent d\u2019une mani\u00e8re injurieuse de ce qu\u2019ils ignorent, et ils p\u00e9riront par leur propre corruption,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.13","name":"2 Pierre 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.11","name":"2 Pierre 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.13","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:13","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>recevant ainsi le salaire de leur iniquit\u00e9. Ils trouvent leurs d\u00e9lices \u00e0 se livrer au plaisir en plein jour; hommes tar\u00e9s et souill\u00e9s, ils se d\u00e9lectent dans leurs tromperies, en faisant bonne ch\u00e8re avec vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.14","name":"2 Pierre 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.12","name":"2 Pierre 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.14","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:14","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ils ont les yeux pleins d\u2019adult\u00e8re et insatiables de p\u00e9ch\u00e9; ils amorcent les \u00e2mes mal affermies; ils ont le c\u0153ur exerc\u00e9 \u00e0 la cupidit\u00e9; ce sont des enfants de mal\u00e9diction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.15","name":"2 Pierre 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.13","name":"2 Pierre 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.15","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:15","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir quitt\u00e9 le droit chemin, ils se sont \u00e9gar\u00e9s en suivant la voie de Balaam, fils de Bosor, qui aima le salaire de l\u2019iniquit\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.16","name":"2 Pierre 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.14","name":"2 Pierre 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.16","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:16","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>mais qui fut repris pour sa transgression: une \u00e2nesse muette, faisant entendre une voix d\u2019homme, arr\u00eata la d\u00e9mence du proph\u00e8te.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.17","name":"2 Pierre 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.15","name":"2 Pierre 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.17","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:17","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ces gens-l\u00e0 sont des fontaines sans eau, des nu\u00e9es que chasse un tourbillon: l\u2019obscurit\u00e9 des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres leur est r\u00e9serv\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.18","name":"2 Pierre 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.16","name":"2 Pierre 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.18","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:18","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Avec des discours enfl\u00e9s de vanit\u00e9, ils amorcent par les convoitises de la chair, par les dissolutions, ceux qui viennent \u00e0 peine d\u2019\u00e9chapper aux hommes qui vivent dans l\u2019\u00e9garement;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.19","name":"2 Pierre 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.17","name":"2 Pierre 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.19","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:19","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>ils leur promettent la libert\u00e9, quand ils sont eux-m\u00eames esclaves de la corruption, car chacun est esclave de ce qui a triomph\u00e9 de lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.20","name":"2 Pierre 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.18","name":"2 Pierre 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.20","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:20","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>En effet, si, apr\u00e8s s\u2019\u00eatre retir\u00e9s des souillures du monde, par la connaissance du Seigneur et Sauveur J\u00e9sus-Christ, ils s\u2019y engagent de nouveau et sont vaincus, leur derni\u00e8re condition est pire que la premi\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.21","name":"2 Pierre 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.19","name":"2 Pierre 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.21","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:21","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.002.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Car mieux valait pour eux n\u2019avoir pas connu la voie de la justice, que de se d\u00e9tourner, apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir connue, du saint commandement qui leur avait \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.22","name":"2 Pierre 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.20","name":"2 Pierre 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.22","label":"","reference":"2 Pierre 2:22","prev_osis_id":"2Pet.002.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Pet.2.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Il leur est arriv\u00e9 ce que dit un proverbe vrai: Le chien est retourn\u00e9 \u00e0 ce qu\u2019il avait vomi, et la truie lav\u00e9e s\u2019est vautr\u00e9e dans le bourbier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2","name":"2 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.3.1","name":"2 Pierre 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.2.21","name":"2 Pierre 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.2.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc82c8aa1.63072725');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc82c8aa1.63072725\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc82c8aa1.63072725","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc82c8aa1.63072725'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc82c8aa1.63072725\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}